POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/compare?meaning=동.사랑하다,좋아하다/명.사랑&user_input=동.사랑하다,좋아하다/명.사랑
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. 불완전한 품사 입력 테스트
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/compare?meaning=사랑,좋아해&user_input=동.
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. 단어장에 단어 추가
